Program: Discovery
Title: Robots - part four
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03jry2g
Last Broadcast Date: 30 April 2002
An investigation into the robots of the future. How robotics are being used to help people with injuries or disabilities. The programme examines the Locomat, a computerized walking equipment with robot control used for rehabilitation. Picture: Woman using robotic legs to aid walking, Credit: Getty Images Show less